# Pesto Bacon Deviled Eggs

> #app #snack

![](89F37E64-73A5-4BCF-AA30-2981007CD943.jpeg)

- Eggs | 12 | Hard boiled, peeled
- Mayonnaise | 1/4 cup | 
- Pesto | 2 tbsp | 
- Lemon | 1 tsp | Juiced
- Bacon | 2 slices | Cooked, chopped

Mix yolks with 1/4 cup mayo, 2 tablespoons pesto, and 1 teaspoon lemon juice. Spoon into whites; top with crumbled cooked bacon.
